msgid "Add the following to your ``pyproject.toml``:"
msgstr "Ajoutez les éléments suivants à votre ``pyproject.toml``:"

#: ../../source/how-to-configure-pyproject-toml.rst:176
msgid ""
"When you execute |flwr_run_cli_link|_ or |flwr_build_cli_link|_, the "
"resulting FAB will contain ``pyproject.toml``, "
"``your_module/client_app.py``, ``your_module/server_app.py``, and "
"``conf/config.yaml`` — but not ``your_module/scratch.py`` or "
"``README.md``."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque vous exécutez |flwr_run_cli_link|_ ou |flwr_build_cli_link|_, le "
"FAB résultant contiendra ``pyproject.toml``, "
"``your_module/client_app.py``, ``your_module/server_app.py``, et "
"``conf/config.yaml`` — mais pas ``your_module/scratch.py`` ou "
