msgstr "Migrer vos workloads OpenFL vers Flower dans ce guide étape par étape"

#: ../../source/how-to-migrate-from-openfl.rst:45
msgid "OpenFL Migration Guide"
msgstr "Guide de migration OpenFL"

#: ../../source/how-to-migrate-from-openfl.rst:47
msgid ""
"It was `recently announced "
"<https://github.com/securefederatedai/openfederatedlearning>`_ that The "
"Open Federated Learning project (formerly known as OpenFL) is no longer "
"being developed or maintained. This guide, written in collaboration with "
"the OpenFL developers, aims to create an easy path for OpenFL users to "
"bring their workloads into Flower."
msgstr ""
"C'est `recently announced "
"<https://github.com/securefederatedai/openfederatedlearning>`_ qui a "
"déclaré que le projet Open Federated Learning (anciennement connu sous le"
" nom d'OpenFL) n'est plus développé ou maintenu. Ce guide, rédigé en "
"collaboration avec les développeurs OpenFL, vise à créer un chemin facile"
" pour les utilisateurs OpenFL pour apporter leurs workloads dans Flower."

#: ../../source/how-to-migrate-from-openfl.rst:55
msgid "Creating a Flower App for OpenFL code"
msgstr "Créer une application Flower pour le code OpenFL"

#: ../../source/how-to-migrate-from-openfl.rst:57
