#: ../../source/ref-changelog.md:217
msgid ""
"**Introduce local SuperLink for managing local simulations** "
"([#6599](https://github.com/flwrlabs/flower/pull/6599), "
"[#6717](https://github.com/flwrlabs/flower/pull/6717))"
msgstr ""
"**Introduit SuperLink local pour gérer les simulations locales** "
"([#6599](https://github.com/flwrlabs/flower/pull/6599), "
"[#6717](https://github.com/flwrlabs/flower/pull/6717))"

#: ../../source/ref-changelog.md:219
msgid ""
"Local simulations are now managed by a local SuperLink, which is "
"automatically launched on demand. This enables running most `flwr` CLI "
"commands locally, such as `flwr list` to list previous runs and `flwr "
"log` to retrieve logs from earlier runs. See the "
"[documentation](https://flower.ai/docs/framework/1.27/en/how-to-run-"
"flower-locally.html) for more details."
msgstr ""
"Les simulations locales sont maintenant gérées par un SuperLink local, "
"qui est lancé automatiquement à la demande. Cela permet d'exécuter la "
"plupart des commandes CLI `flwr` localement, telles que `flwr list` pour "
"afficher les runs précédents et `flwr log` pour récupérer les logs de "
"runs antérieurs. Voir la "
"[documentation](https://flower.ai/docs/framework/1.27/en/how-to-run-"
"flower-locally.html)) pour plus de détails."

#: ../../source/ref-changelog.md:221
msgid ""
"**Allow SuperLink log rotation** "
"([#6700](https://github.com/flwrlabs/flower/pull/6700))"
msgstr ""
"**Autoriser la rotation des journaux SuperLink** "
"([#6700](https://github.com/flwrlabs/flower/pull/6700)))"

#: ../../source/ref-changelog.md:223
msgid ""
"Adds support for timed log rotation in SuperLink. Log files can now be "
"configured using `--log-file`, `--log-rotation-interval-hours`, and "
"`--log-rotation-backup-count`."
msgstr ""
"Ajoute le support de la rotation des journaux en fonction du temps dans "
"SuperLink. Les fichiers journaux peuvent maintenant être configurés à "
"l'aide de `--log-file`, `--log-rotation-interval-hours` et `--log-"
"rotation-backup-count`."

