#: ../../source/ref-changelog.md:405
msgid ""
"Introduces a unified heartbeat mechanism for app processes, preventing "
"hangs when an app process crashes without responding. The new system "
"enables `flwr-serverapp` and `flwr-simulation` processes to exit more "
"quickly when a run is stopped by the `flwr stop` command."
msgstr ""
"Introduces a unified heartbeat mechanism for app processes, preventing "
"hangs when an app process crashes without responding. The new system "
"enables `flwr-serverapp` and `flwr-simulation` processes to exit more "
"quickly when a run is stopped by the `flwr stop` command."

