"The `flwr run`, `flwr ls`, and `flwr stop` commands now support JSON-"
"formatted sortie using the `--format json` flag. This makes it easier to "
"parse and integrate CLI sortie with other tools. Feel free to check the "
"[\"How to Use CLI JSON "
"sortie\"](https://flower.ai/docs/framework/v1.14.0/en/how-to-use-cli-"
"json-sortie.html) guide for details!"

