"XGBoost is a tree-based ensemble machine learning algorithm that uses "
"gradient boosting to improve model accuracy. We added a new `FedXgbNnAvg`"
" "
"[strategy](https://github.com/flwrlabs/flower/tree/main/src/py/flwr/server/strategy/fedxgb_nn_avg.py),"
" and a [code "
"example](https://github.com/flwrlabs/flower/tree/main/examples/xgboost-"
"quickstart) that demonstrates the usage of this new strategy in an "
"XGBoost project."

