#: ../../source/ref-changelog.md:2123
msgid ""
"`Adam Narozniak`, `Alexander Viala Bellander`, `Charles Beauville`, "
"`Daniel J. Beutel`, `JDRanpariya`, `Lennart Behme`, `Taner Topal`"
msgstr ""
"`Adam Narozniak`, `Alexander Viala Bellander`, `Charles Beauville`, "
