"will generate all the files needed to run a federation of 10 nodes using "
"|fedxgbbagging_link|_ strategy. By default, the generated app uses a "
"local simulation profile that ``flwr run`` submits to a managed local "
"SuperLink, which then executes the run with the Flower Simulation "
"Runtime. The dataset will be partitioned using Flower Dataset's "
"`IidPartitioner <https://flower.ai/docs/datasets/ref-"
"api/flwr_datasets.partitioner.IidPartitioner.html#flwr_datasets.partitioner.IidPartitioner>`_."
msgstr ""
