"we want to decrease the learning rate by a factor of 0.5 every 5 rounds, "
"then we need to override the ``configure_train`` method of our strategy "
"and embed such logic."
msgstr ""
"Au |strategy_start_link|_ méthode de notre stratégie, on nous passe déjà "
"un |configrecord_link|_ spécifiant le taux d'apprentissage initial. Ce "
"``ConfigRecord`` sera envoyé aux clients dans toutes les ``Messages`` "
