"15 pour voir la décadence du taux d'apprentissage en action."

#: ../../source/tutorial-series-use-a-federated-learning-strategy-pytorch.rst:318
msgid ""
"You'll note that in the ``configure_train`` stage of rounds 5 and 10, the"
